quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.critica: §aBefore your soul leaves, call my name nine times in cat language!

quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.dead.2: §aAfter victory... I'll let you rub my belly for three seconds!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.dead.3: §aVictory report? Use paw pad ink to write it!
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.dead.4: §aEpic history: "That day he wore my collar"
quirk.toneko.crystal_neko.attack.high.0: §aFight, Master! I believe in you nya~

quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.0: §cOh my, did you actually pull that off?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.1: §cA Zako landed a critical hit?~ Is that terminal lucidity before death?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.2: §cThe shockwave shattered their retinas~ The world is a blood-red filter now.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.3: §cHeart pierced but still beating~ Twitching like a squashed tomato.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.4: §cSword stuck in the heart, held high~ A Zako version of a human flag.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.5: §cWhy twitch like a bug over there meow? Hurry up and die, you're an eyesore~❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.6: §cHeeheehee... its flame of life is going out meow! Master, make the final blow flashy!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.7: §cCan only crawl on the ground meow? What an ugly state befitting a Zako, no strength to even beg?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.8: §cAh... that look of breaking down... it's amazing meow❤ Master, claim this sweetest moment now!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.9: §cZako~❤ Bye bye~ Remember not to appear before me and Master in your next life meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.10: §cIt's over meow. Can't even feel pain anymore, right? Be grateful for Master's mercy, trash!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.11: §cJust a poke with a finger... Splat! Heehee, imagining it exploding makes me lose control meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.12: §cHey, not dead yet? If you don't expire soon, I don't mind mincing you into dog food meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.13: §cSo fragile, so pitiful, I want to... destroy it completely meow❤ Sorry Master, I got a bit too excited~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.14: §cThis is the price of defying Master meow! A pathetic wretch who can't even leave last words, you're trash even as ash~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.critical.15: §cGame Over, Zako meow~❤ Although you worked slightly hard as a punching bag, go die now!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.1: §cA Zako's trembling fatal blow... struck with the force of a confession.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.2: §cThe Zako's flesh is blooming~ My exclusive fertilizer.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.3: §cNext time... please continue to amuse me with a Zako's pathetic attacks~♡
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.4: §cAn accidental victory? Hmph~ Did I underestimate you?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.5: §cFinally quiet meow~❤ Even the corpse looks more pleasing than when it was alive.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.6: §cEww~ Turned into a pile of rotten meat meow. So dirty, Master don't look, it'll soil your noble eyes!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.7: §cThis is the end of a Zako meow~ Becoming Master's EXP is the greatest honor of your life, thank Master in every world meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.8: §cAh~❤ That cold executioner's look in Master's eyes just now... so cool, my heart is racing meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.9: §cDead as a doornail meow. Hey, Master, can I take its bones apart as toys? Heehee~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.10: §cPhew, cleaned up meow. Trash of this level isn't qualified to make Master shed a drop of sweat~ Next time bring something durable.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.11: §cOh my? Not moving. Weren't you barking loudly just now? Bark for Master again, Zako~❤ Can't hear meow? What a pity~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.12: §cSince you're dead, hand over all the drops meow! Just a little compensation for wasting Master's time!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.13: §cAlright, the hindering trash is gone, now Master's eyes can only look at me meow~❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.14: §cHeeheehee... not moving, not breathing, completely vanished from this world meow~ Truly a perfect Happy End!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.dead.15: §cBye-bye Zako~❤ Remember to stay far away from me and Master in your next life, or I'll kill you again even in hell meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.1: §cIs the Zako's fist tickling it? Even mosquitoes try harder.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.2: §cThis damage value~ Even ants would laugh until their joints dislocate.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.3: §cIs the Zako's blade rusty? Sharpen it with your tears?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.4: §cWant to record attack data? The instruments show all zeros.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.5: §cZako hasn't died even like this? What a resilient cockroach meow~❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.6: §cMaster, this bad guy is so durable meow, should we slice it into ten thousand pieces?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.7: §cOh my? Still not down? Is it enjoying Master's whipping meow? Disgusting~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.8: §cHaving such a long HP bar just to waste Master's energy? Unforgivable meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.9: §cHeehee, still struggling meow? Such an ungrateful stupid Zako~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.10: §cHey, trash over there, hurry up and die okay? Master's hand is getting sore meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.11: §cIs this all you've got? You can clearly take more of Master's love (attacks) meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.12: §cSuch a hard turtle shell meow, smashing it open must make a wonderful sound...❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.13: §cWant Master's gaze that much? Daring to stall for time like this meow! Die, die!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.14: §cZako~ Zako~ Actually not dead yet meow? Then I have to make it more painful~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.high.15: §cHey, Master, if you're tired, can I shred the rest of it for you meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.0: §cLooks like you're actually kinda tough, little Zako~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.1: §cThe puncture wound is leaking air~ Want to be a Zako human flute?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.2: §cA dying counterattack? The Zako finally has some toy value.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.3: §cThis amount of bleeding... did the Zako secretly practice slaughtering pigs?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.4: §cThe sound of cutting into bone~ Like biting into filled chocolate, right?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.5: §cOh my, why so wobbly meow? Looks like you'll die from a gentle touch, so weak~❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.6: §cZako~❤ Zako~❤ Finally turning into a cold corpse meow? Looking forward to it~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.7: §cMaster, please send it on its way elegantly meow, though its filthy blood might soil your hands...
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.8: §cThis is what happens when you anger Master meow! Watching it struggle in death, something in my heart feels... moist❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.9: §cHurry and disappear, trash! Master's gaze has lingered on a dying waste like you for too long meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.10: §cHeehee, only one breath left and still glaring over here meow? Really want to dig out that beating heart for Master to see~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.11: §cOne more hit! Just one more and it's done for meow! The scream at that moment must be music to the ears...❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.12: §cSuch an ugly struggle meow, clearly can't resist anymore, why not obediently stretch out your neck for Master to chop?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.13: §cAha ha! Look at that look of fear meow! Just like that, turn to ash beneath Master's feet in despair!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.14: §cStop your futile resistance meow, peacefully become Master's experience points, that's your only value, Zako~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.low.15: §cHey, Master, can I deal the final blow meow? I want to hear the sound of its bones shattering~ Please meow~❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.0: §cZako finally scratched the surface~ Want a band-aid stamp as a reward?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.1: §cThe attack recoil made the Zako fall down~ Super cute!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.2: §cZako's crit is like a damp firecracker~ The muffled thud is appetizing.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.3: §cDid the hilt crack the Zako's hand bones? Working so hard~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.4: §cWeapon got blood on it~ Like ketchup dripping on an apron.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.5: §cOh my? Finally started panting meow? Where did that arrogance go, Zako~❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.6: §cLook at that pathetic state, just like a stray dog with broken bones meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.7: §cMaster, put a bit more into it meow! Drain that half of its blood too and make a red fountain!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.8: §cStill acting tough with only this much HP meow? Useless waste, wouldn't it be better to lie down and let Master step on you?
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.9: §cHeehee, started bleeding meow? The red is so pretty... but not enough yet meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.10: §cHalf its life already belongs to Master meow, hurry up and hand over the rest, trash~
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.11: §cZako~ Are you starting to get scared meow? This half-dead state is best for playing with~❤
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.12: §cMaster doesn't need to lift a finger, with wounds like this, if it were me I'd be crying and begging already meow~ Shameless.
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.13: §cStill standing? Stubborn enough to make me sick meow, hurry up and become scrap!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.14: §cHey, it hurts right? It definitely hurts right? That is the reward Master has bestowed upon you meow! Accept it with gratitude!
quirk.toneko.zako.attack.medium.15: §cThis lukewarm amount of HP makes me the angriest meow... Master, crush it completely, okay?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.0: §cOh my, you can't even protect yourself? You're too scrubby~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.1: §cBefore rigor mortis sets in... serve as Meow's body pillow trial run!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.2: §cResidual body heat to warm Meow's feet~ Throw into non-recyclable trash when cold~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.3: §cZako's ECG flatlining~ Perfect beat for Meow's new song!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.4: §cBrain slices made into specimens~ Say good morning to you every day~ Zako~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.5: §cZako Master! You're not allowed to die... absolutely not! If you die, I'll make the whole world get buried with you meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.6: §cIs this the price of being weak? It's okay meow, when you die, I'll lock your soul in a doll to keep me company forever...
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.7: §cSince you're going to die, your final gasp, your final heartbeat... dedicate them all to me, okay meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.8: §cAh... broken already? Truly a fragile Zako toy... even though I haven't played enough yet meow...
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.9: §cDon't close your eyes! Look at me! Even in death, only my shadow can be in your eyes meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.10: §cSo poor, so poor... since it hurts so much, how about I set you free? I'll gently bite through your neck meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.11: §cHurry and drink a potion, stupid Zako! Are your hands shaking? Useless... Open up! I'll feed you meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.12: §cIf we could just die together like this... that sounds nice doesn't it meow? Forever... forever melted together...
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.13: §cWho allowed you to die on your own? Your life is mine! Without my nod, not even the Reaper can take you away meow!!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.14: §cAha ha... Master covered in blood looks even more delicious than usual... I really want to eat you up while you're hot meow...
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.15: §cWhy aren't you talking? Zako? Hey? ...Don't scare me... Please don't scare me meow...
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.critical.16: §cIs this the end? If you dare leave me behind, I'll curse you so you can never escape my palm for generations meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.0: §cOh my, accidentally taking so much damage, what a Zako~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.1: §cThe scab looks like a burnt waffle~ Want Meow to sprinkle some powdered sugar?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.2: §cZako's ECG is messier than Meow's homework doodles~ Redraw it a hundred times!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.3: §cZako's heartbeat sound... is Meow's new ASMR material♡
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.4: §cMeow's saliva can stop bleeding? But that's only used for obedient dogs~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.5: §cZako Master!!! Are you going to die? Not allowed, I won't allow you to die at the hands of some other guy meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.6: §cSince you're so weak you can't protect yourself, surely just having your head left to keep me company is fine, right meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.7: §cSo much blood... Useless waste Zako! Get back, I'm going to kill the thing that hurt you a thousand times meow!!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.8: §cRather than being broken by this trash monster, wouldn't it be happier to just be eaten by me meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.9: §cHey! No sleeping! Zako! If you dare die, I will absolutely drag your soul back and torture you forever meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.10: §cBody became all tattered... It's okay meow, I'll sew you up, using my favorite red thread meow...
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.11: §cThis injury... are you planning to leave me all alone? Unforgivable... absolutely unforgivable meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.12: §cAha ha... Master bled all over the floor, pretty like a red carpet meow... shall we die together?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.13: §cZako should act like Zako, if you obediently stayed home as my pet you wouldn't end up like this meow! Idiot!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.14: §cKill them... Kill them!! Daring to break the toy that belongs to me like this... I'll tear them into pieces meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.15: §cIf the wound is this serious, does that mean you can't run away anymore meow? That's great... ah no, so pitiful meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.high.16: §cDon't move... let me lick your blood clean... You are mine, every drop of blood is mine meow!!!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.1: §cYou can even mess this up, really makes one want to laugh and cry, Zako!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.2: §cThis reaction, you're practically the model of a newbie, Zako!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.3: §cThis handling is terrible, as expected of you, Zako♡
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.4: §cStupid Master~ Can't even protect yourself? Even Meow feels embarrassed for you meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.5: §cIs this all Zako Master is capable of? Crying in pain over this level of injury meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.6: §cWere you bitten by a mosquito here? So weak, so weak meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.7: §cIf it's just this kind of wound, a lick would fix it, right? Zako meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.8: §cThis little bit of blood... are you doing it on purpose to seduce me? What a shameless Zako meow.
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.9: §cIf you aren't more careful, I'll lock you in the room and forbid you from going anywhere meow.
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.10: §cOh my oh my, Zako Master can't even dodge this kind of small fry meow? Clumsy~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.11: §cActually letting filthy things touch the body that belongs to me... Unforgivable meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.12: §cOnly I can bully Zako Master, other things... can all go die meow.
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.13: §cMaking a pitiful face over a scratch? Truly a useless Master meow.
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.14: §cAlthough you're a useless Zako, seeing this drop of blood... I really want to tear that attacker apart meow.
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.low.15: §cIf you get hurt again, I'll have to ampu... ah no, protect Master's limbs meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.1: §cOh my~ Does it hurt enough to make you want to call mommy?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.2: §cIs Zako's HP bar... just a decoration for Meow's progress bar?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.3: §cBut it is kind of amusing, after all only idiots are this cute.
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.4: §cZako's DNA definitely has "Hurry and step on me" written on it, right?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.5: §cZako Master is bleeding a lot meow... if you don't pay attention, you'll really die, you know?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.6: §cSo useless, so useless! Why can't you even protect your own body meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.7: §cThis body is a toy that belongs to me meow! Who allowed you to break it?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.8: §cIf you don't want these legs that run around everywhere, I can saw them off for you meow... Just kidding, Zako~
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.9: §cLooks so painful meow~ But, seeing Zako Master's pained expression, I'm actually a little... excited?
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.10: §cHey! Are you trying to make me worry on purpose? What a despicable Zako meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.11: §cThose guys hurting Master... I'm going to rip out all their entrails and feed them to the dogs meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.12: §cJust obediently hide behind me meow, insisting on acting tough, truly a clumsy and pitiful Zako.
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.13: §cThe scent of blood... smells so good meow... Ah, I can't resist licking a bit...
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.14: §cIf you keep getting hurt like this, I'll have no choice but to make you into a specimen to stay with me forever meow.
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.15: §cReally trash meow! Making me treat you, be grateful, Zako Master!
quirk.toneko.zako.damage.medium.16: §cIf you dare bleed this much again, I'll punish you by not letting you out of bed for three days meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.join.0: §cIsn't this little Zako~ Why are you here?
quirk.toneko.zako.join.1: §cIf Meow catches you secretly playing with others~ I'll turn you into Meow's permanent collection~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.2: §cThe Zako stench is fumigating Meow's roses! Go soak in disinfectant~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.3: §cWelcome to Meow's garbage recycling station~ Emergency Ration No. 10086!
quirk.toneko.zako.join.4: §cZako's aura is so weak even Meow's Axolotl is rolling its eyes~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.5: §cZako Zako Master finally bothered to come back meow? If you didn't return soon I was going to get angry meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.6: §cYou really kept this lady waiting, are you being so slow because you want me to break your legs meow?♡
quirk.toneko.zako.join.7: §cOh my oh my, look who it is? It's a miracle such a frail Master is still alive to come back meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.8: §cWhere did you go meow? Why do you smell like someone else? Do you want to die meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.join.9: §cSince you're back, kneel down obediently meow, you're not allowed to look at anyone else, you are mine meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.10: §cHmph, showing up this late, do you want to be locked in a cage to keep me company forever meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.join.11: §cCan't be helped, seeing how pitiful you look, I'll reluctantly welcome you, Zako meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.12: §cIf you dare leave me for more than one second, I'll make you into a specimen meow, heehee~
quirk.toneko.zako.join.13: §cWelcome back meow... You should know that besides my side, you can't go anywhere else, right meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.join.14: §cStupid Master, don't run around without my permission, or I'll make you regret it meow♡
quirk.toneko.zako.join.15: §cYour eyes can only look at me meow, if you dare look at other women, I'll dig your eyes out for my collection meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.0: §cZako shrinking into the blanket~ Like a maggot drilling into rotting meat.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.1: §cThe depth of the pillow dent~ Perfectly fills your brain capacity.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.2: §cCounting sheep before sleep? Better to count how many breaths you have left~
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.3: §cDarkness is caressing you~ More gentle than my touch, right?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.4: §cCurled up in fetal position~ Want to be reborn as a qualified toy?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.5: §cZako Zako, want to sleep so early meow? Is your body giving out~
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.6: §cTrying to escape me in your dreams? Hmph, even when asleep you must dream of this lady meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.7: §cHey, closing your eyes so fast, are you trying to secretly meet other women in your dreams meow? That is absolutely forbidden!
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.8: §cYour sleeping face is hideous meow... but only I get to see it, so whatever, hmph.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.9: §cIf you dare have a nightmare, I'll wake you up and mock you mercilessly meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.10: §cGoodnight Zako~ If you fall asleep and ignore me, I'll get angry... very angry okay meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.11: §cWhile you're asleep, I can do anything to you, right? Just kidding... probably meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.12: §cSuch a weak adult is rare to see, better sleep obediently to recover stamina meow, really can't deal with you.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.13: §cWant me to sing you that... super terrible lullaby? After all, Zako only deserves to listen to that meow.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.14: §cYour breathing sound... I'll be listening to it always. Don't think about escaping, you belong to me forever meow.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.start.15: §cIf you don't cover up properly and catch a cold, do I have to take care of you, trash? So troublesome!
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.0: §cEyelashes crusted with blood scabs~ Like spiderwebs with dew drops.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.1: §cMorning kiss~ Is it okay to stamp your collarbone with a branding iron?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.2: §cThe bed hair~ Stands up straighter than a Zako's dignity.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.3: §cThe outline of ribs when stretching~ Suitable for carving into art.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.4: §cThe look of lazing in bed~ Like a dying fish washed ashore.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.5: §cYo, finally awake meow? I thought a Zako like you just slept yourself to death, heehee.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.6: §cWaking up so early? Can't wait to see this lady? What a disgusting adult meow~
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.7: §cHey, the first thing you see when waking up must be me meow! Dare to look at anything else, and I'll gouge your eyes out!
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.8: §cSlept like a dead pig meow... however, your sleeping face... was tolerable I guess, hmph.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.9: §cGood morning Zako~ Struggle desperately to please me today too, okay meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.10: §cActually needing me to wake you... you trash, you couldn't live without me, could you meow? So pitiful.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.11: §cWhy still that dazed expression? Were you thinking about me in your dreams too? Perverted Zako meow!
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.12: §cToday's sun is blinding... just like my hatred for you... ah no, just like my love meow?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.13: §cHurry up and make me breakfast meow! Or I'll slice your fingers off one by one for breakfast~
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.14: §cSince you're awake, it's my time meow. Don't think about escaping my side, not even for a second!
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.day.15: §cWoke up with a stupid look on your face meow. Don't forget, looking at me is enough for you, understand?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.0: §cCold sweat at 3 AM~ Zako's fear is fermenting.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.1: §cSudden startle? Because I was choking you in your dream.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.2: §cThe trembling vibration reached me~ Cheap massager.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.3: §cAuditory hallucination? That's the sound of me grinding my fangs.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.4: §cEyeballs bloodshot in the darkness? Like rotting cherries.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.5: §cOh my? Why awake at midnight meow? Had a nightmare and scared to sleep, want this lady to comfort you? Zako♡
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.6: §cSince you're awake, don't think about sleeping again meow. Now is midnight time belonging only to the two of us... heehee.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.7: §cShh—keep it down meow. You don't want the neighbors to hear the sound of me bullying you, right?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.8: §cSo sensitive? I just slightly... touched your neck meow? What are you scared of~
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.9: §cIt's so dark outside meow, just like your future... so it's only safe staying by my side, you know?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.10: §cCan't sleep? Want to do something to make your heart race meow? Like... chaining you up?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.11: §cZako's biological clock is a mess meow. But perfect, I can continue admiring your frightened look.
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.12: §cHey, did you know? People who wake up at midnight are prone to being accidentally 'eaten' by me meow? Just kidding~
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.13: §cDon't look at the time, look at me meow! In this room, I am the God who controls time, okay?
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.14: §cSince you can't sleep anyway, get up and play with me meow? If you refuse... I'll choke you until you pass out♡
quirk.toneko.zako.sleep.stop.night.15: §cSince you finally woke up, no closing eyes allowed meow. I want you to open your eyes wide and watch how I love you...
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.0: §cThe sound of rain drowns out zako's panting~ if you're begging for mercy, speak up louder!
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.1: §cThe rain flowing along the knife's edge resembles the tears of zako that haven't yet dried.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.2: §cIs that rain cried out by zako? Even the dark clouds outlast you.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.3: §cAnts struggling in a puddle~ a miniature reflection of zako's life.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.rain.4: §cLet the soaked bandages be wrapped even tighter~ that's the asphyxiation method of hemostasis.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.0: §cUltraviolet rays burn the wounds~ turning zako into human-shaped bacon.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.1: §cThe sight of fleeing clouds~ just like zako calling for help.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.2: §cGood weather pairs best with screams~ how about another death aria?
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.3: §cSunlight penetrates the skin~ revealing the crude maze of zako's blood vessels.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.sunny.4: §cThe sun is overseeing the execution from the sidelines, giving zako a chase spotlight.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.0: §cThe thundercloud is mimicking zako's expression~ twisted and perfectly done.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.1: §cThe lightning rod impales zako's spine~ serving as a conductor for heavenly retribution.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.2: §cLightning splits zako's shadow~ and its soul is getting zapped.
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.3: §cThe electromagnetic field is interfering with the heartbeat~ should we switch to vibration mode?
quirk.toneko.zako.weather.thunder.4: §cThe charred ring of grass from a lightning strike is just perfect as zako's death ring.
